# OSMM working instances
# Per CONVENTION.md, object instances produced during client work or internal
# testing live OUTSIDE the repo until validated and promoted into examples/.
# Ignore stray JSON at the repo root and in a local scratch dir so unvalidated
# instances are never committed by accident. Validated examples under examples/
# are explicitly re-included below.
/*.json
/scratch/
!examples/**/*.json
